Vision: Next 9

What It Is (1-2 sentences)

A web application designed to eliminate creative block for visual content creators by using AI to generate a cohesive 3x3 grid of image ideas based on a single style reference.

Who It's For (1-2 sentences)

Visual content creators and social media managers who prioritize aesthetic consistency and need a fast, iterative tool to generate on-brand post ideas.

The Core Experience

Users upload an inspiration image, generate a grid of 9 new posts matching that style, and then "mix-and-match" by keeping their favorite images while regenerating the rest based on new inspiration.

Out of Scope for MVP

User accounts or profile management.

Integration with social media platforms (sharing is via native download).

Historical archives or saving past grids.

In-app analytics or tracking.

Settings pages or advanced filtering.
